Silverback is located in Chapel Hill, North Carolina, part of the Research Triangle, and is easily accessible by the Raleigh-Durham International Airport (RDU). We welcome investor visits to our office, and have put together a downloadable information packet to assist you in your travel planning. You can also explore the links below for additional information.

