									Driving Directions:
From RDU Airport and East:
Take I-40 West approximately 13 miles. Take Exit 273A (Hwy 54 West towards Chapel Hill). Go about 2.5 miles and turn left at the 6th traffic light. That is The Exchange at Meadowmont (SunTrust Building). We are in Suite 250, located on the second floor.
From Greensboro and West:
Take I-40 East toward Chapel Hill. Take Exit 273A (Hwy 54 West towards Chapel HIll). Go about 2.5 miles and turn left at the 6th traffic light. That is The Exchange at Meadowmont (SunTrust Building). We are in Suite 250, located on the second floor.
								

