            Silverback Asset Management, LLC is an alternative investment firm that specializes in managing arbitrage and relative value strategies for institutional investors. Silverback's expertise spans U.S. credit, equity, and volatility markets. Strategies employed include convertible arbitrage, capital structure arbitrage and equity volatility arbitrage. Silverback was founded in 2002 by Elliot Bossen, who continues to lead the firm. Mr. Bossen has over 28 years of investment experience and has developed a talented investment team. Silverback enjoys a solid business foundation made up of top prime brokers, auditors, administrators, and its strategic partner Investcorp.
          






















