Company Overview of Silverback Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Silverback Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles and institutional investors. It invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets of the United States. The firm employs convertible arbitrage, capital structure arbitrage, and equity volatility arbitrage strategies to make investments. Silverback Asset Management was founded in 2002 and is based in Chapel Hill, North Carolina.


